posts.subject: New Content - Response
posts.body: Seriously tho. It's almost as if her sets are top secret or something because i cannot find anything new, maybe people just don't wanna share

"I believe if somebody was to leak the topless pics right away that would be a very dumb idea. She herself has said that if she finds out that somebody is leaking her topless stuff, she'll stop doing them immediately, which is something I believe nobody wants her to do. So what I'm saying is, if you're going to leak her 150$ tier, don't. Not right now anyways."
